                  NoClassDefFoundError.class,
                  () -> RestAssuredResponseOptionsGroovyImplDirectAccess
                          .resolveWithCompilerGeneratedClassResolver(missingClassName));
  
          assertEquals(missingClassName, error.getMessage());
      }
  }
